          <h2>Can I host or facilitate a coderetreat?</h2>
          <p>Yes you can! To get started, fill in the <a href="http://bit.ly/gdcr14_leader_reg">host and facilitator registration form</a> and we will give you access to leaders-only mailing lists and other resources to help you plan your coderetreat.</p>
          <p>Do you have questions about hosting a coderetreat, or are you unsure if you want to host? Feel free to check out our <a href="hosts/faq.html">Hosting FAQ</a>.</p>

          <h2>Who is organizing this?</h2>
          <p>GDCR 2014 will be brought to you by hundreds of passionate local hosts and facilitators worldwide and a team of global coordinators, including <a href="https://twitter.com/jthurne" target="_blank">Jim Hurne</a>, <a href="https://twitter.com/adibolb" target="_blank">Adi Bolboaca</a>, <a href="https://twitter.com/martinklose" target="_blank">Martin Klose</a>, and <a href="https://twitter.com/ElenaYankova1" target="_blank">Elena Yankova</a>.</p>
